BEST EVER LINE TO  KEEP IN MIND WHENEVER YOU HEAR ABOUT KADANE'S ALGO:
we will keep the subarray sum with us as long as the sum is +ve....the moment it becomes -ve we will update it with 0....and move on to the later of the array.
